<p>–≤ views/index.erb –≤ —Ñ–æ—Ä–º–µ –∑–∞–º–µ–Ω–∏–º —Å—Ç–∞—Ç–∏—á–µ—Å–∫–∏–µ –¥–∞–Ω–Ω—ã–µ –Ω–∞ :</p>
<div class="language-ruby highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>&lt;p&gt;
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>  &lt;select name=<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">option</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span>&gt;
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>    &lt;option value=<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span> selected&gt;–í—ã–±—Ä–∞—Ç—å –æ–ø—Ü–∏—é...&lt;<span style="background-color:hsla(300,100%,50%,0.06)"><span style="color:#404">/</span><span style="color:#808">option&gt;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span><span style="background-color:hsla(300,100%,50%,0.06)"><span style="color:#808">    &lt;% @options.each do |item| %&gt;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span><span style="background-color:hsla(300,100%,50%,0.06)"><span style="color:#808">    &lt;option value=&quot;&lt;%= item['option'] %&gt;&quot;&gt;&lt;%= item['option'] %&gt;&lt;</span><span style="color:#404">/</span><span style="color:#C2C">o</span></span>ption&gt;
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>    &lt;<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">% </span><span style="color:#D20">end</span><span style="color:#710"> </span></span>%&gt;
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span>  &lt;<span style="background-color:hsla(300,100%,50%,0.06)"><span style="color:#404">/</span><span style="color:#808">select&gt;</span></span>
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n8" name="n8">8</a></span><span style="background-color:hsla(300,100%,50%,0.06)"><span style="color:#808">&lt;</span><span style="color:#404">/</span></span>p&gt;
</pre></div>
